name: Lana Dingwall
description: I am a core team member and chapter lead with The GreenPill Network, as well as the Head of Growth at Glo Dollar, a stablecoin funding public goods. I serve on the Gitcoin Community Grants Council, have experience with CharmVerse's Grants Team, and am a Council member at Octant and an ambassador for Unlock Protocol. With a strong background in DAOs and community building, I bring expertise in governance and network development, and I am committed to advocating for collaborative solutions to global challenges.
